keyFacts: The document is a photo lineup form from the Palm Beach Police Department dated November 7, 2005.
It is associated with police case number 05-368.
The lineup includes descriptors for six male individuals with partially gray hair, but their names are not provided in the visible text.
Physical descriptors recorded include jacket numbers, booking IDs, hair color, eye color, build, complexion, height, weight, and marital status.
The document is labeled as a copy, indicating it is part of official police records.
